{"tid":427310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 讚 囡 囡 粵 語 有 進 步","createTime":"2017-10-07T11:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T06:18:13.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0c15cc39e72dbce3c5fe974160771fc50cd9407f","tid":427310,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）早前帶囡囡Sofia陪老公Sergio返西班牙探親，兼且放大假。近日已返港工作的GiGi，大前日趁中秋放假跟家人在屋企過，同日更應節放了兩條片上網，其中母女一齊扮貓星人「喵喵」聲叫，點擊極高。Sofia有樣學樣跟媽咪GiGi一起扮貓叫，更舉起招財貓手勢，非常可愛。<br />\n<br />\n另一條應節片，是GiGi利用手機App，將囡囡變身兔仔，對着鏡頭用廣東話跟大家講「中秋節快樂」。平日以英文跟人交流的Sofia，忽然改用廣東話，而且咬字清晰，GiGi亦開心地大讚囡囡「廣東話有進步」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171007/large/1507300008_f1e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171007%2Flarge%2F1507300008_f1e5.jpg&h=0a45586b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGiGi與Sofia扮貓星人拍片，囡囡更在片中講廣東話。"},{"pid":"62b9c991f7a1204ff8df7f3105f41723de488e2c","tid":427310,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36e6f3dfa3608a4c62efa1dfb77a948481119871","tid":427310,"uid":8165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西</span>"},{"pid":"c9d24edfd9e6163241903166a10f984dfeb3c680","tid":427310,"uid":67003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班</span>"},{"pid":"80111ad5f9e68aaca91e849ae6c47ab93967f3ac","tid":427310,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班</span></blockquote><br />\n牙<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"a58c7c4ee5993d3781f9735761338faa93b88264","tid":427310,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班</span></blockquote><br />\n牙<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n牙你老母"},{"pid":"95284caa967c55a6fc979938d90e270d60b98701","tid":427310,"uid":72754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"唔知點解見到佢就特別扯火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7d9dea0c0d7ab98fd3d64831368c32efe21f97","tid":427310,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">西</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班</span></blockquote><br />\n牙<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n牙你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左"},{"pid":"c82546d8e92ca06773c28b13591e92afaee18b06","tid":427310,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e94f96888f8e2e19ba3411b799877054f8c57f19","tid":427310,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"C:/Ser G O.gif"},{"pid":"a707b5f28073c437bb5afcd6caab1c9b4fd096ef","tid":427310,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"西班牙藉老公Sergio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}